content:
WorkItemCallback Delegate

Definition

Represents the method that executes on a separate work item thread.

In this Article

public delegate void WorkItemCallback();
Inheritance
Object
Delegate
WorkItemCallback

Remarks

This delegate is passed to the Post method and provides a callback method for the thread to which the work item is being posted.
